data.description: Step inside to this Beautiful home built in 2022 with open concept living room/ Kitchen with vaulted ceilings. Hardwood look LVP throughout. Kitchen has granite counter tops, stainless appliances and island with sink. Washer and Dryer will remain with the house. Three  spacious Bedrooms and 2 Baths. Master bath has a garden tub and separate shower.  Enjoy your day sitting on your covered patio drinking coffee. House sits on a large lot with plenty of space in the backyard to build a nice workshop that  already has a concrete slab. Don't miss out on this one!
